※NOTE:  art series “ Vectis Company “ now officaly change it’s name into “TheEquion” series, this series shows all the concept of the great fictional universe called “The Equion” , a pony-liked outer space species that will begin the golden age of the galaxy, this universe will become game concept or film and novel idea if it got enough attention, thank you for your supporting
 
Narsil are the high ranked battle units of Equion , in their language alled “Arzenil” , means “The swifted general” , EUN(Earth Unite Nation) officaly named it as “Narsil” in Geneva Galatical Researching Meeting at 2457, the named was named after a famous fantasy novel at 20 centery “The lord of the rings” the sword  “Narsil”
 
Narsil is like the combined unit of MP and Marine Special force, using the T54SilverSheet armor, it’s also the hybird technology product of Equion and Aenon, but as the high ranked unit, it’s armor can directly provide the unit battle adventage, most common one are Cloak, but unlike the orginial cloak, Narsil’s cloak require soliar energy, and because of it’s science principle, the cloaking is more effective under the high light envirement, Dr.Uematsu Haruo comment this cloaking “Shinobi hide themself under the shadow while Narsil hide themself under the light”
 
 
Sean.M & Macaron
